{{Italic title}}
'''''Svensk exegetisk årsbok''''' (''Swedish Exegetical Yearbook'') is an annual [[Peer review|peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] of [[biblical studies]] and [[book review]]s in Swedish and English. It was established in 1936 by the [[Swedish Exegetical Society]] and is distributed internationally by [[Eisenbrauns]]. The [[editor-in-chief]] is [[Göran Eidevall]] ([[Uppsala university]]).

